data.description: This charming end- unit townhome in sought after Lawrenceville boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 and a half bathrooms. The main level features LVP floors throughout, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open concept floor plan seamlessly connects the living room and kitchen making it perfect for entertaining or everyday living. The bright and airy kitchen is equipped with ample cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient breakfast bar. Upstairs, you'll find 3 spacious bedrooms and convenient laundry room is also located on the upper level. This townhome offers the perfect blend of comfort, style and functionality. Don't miss out on this great opportunity! Work will be finished soon. Showings will being and more pictures will be up when contractors are finished.
